'''尼敦·阿倫·迪蘇沙'''（{{lang-pt|'''Nathan Allan de Souza'''}}，{{bd|1996年|3月13日}}），簡稱'''尼敦'''，巴西職業足球員，司職[[翼鋒|翼鋒]]或[[輔鋒|輔鋒]]，現時被[[英超|英超]][[車路士|車路士]]外借至[[巴甲|巴甲]][[米內羅競技俱樂部|明尼路]]，他於2015年7月1日加盟車路士。

==球會生涯==
===帕拉尼恩斯===
尼敦出生於[[圣卡塔琳娜州|圣卡塔琳娜州]][[布盧梅瑙|布盧梅瑙]]，他在2009年以13歲之齡加入[[帕拉尼恩斯|帕拉尼恩斯]]的青年軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.atleticoparanaense.com/site/noticias/detalhe/27524/Sub-17-Reserva-protagonista-Nathan-foi-decisivo-para-o-ttulo-da-Copa-Brasil|title=Sub-17: Reserva protagonista, Nathan foi decisivo para o título da Copa Brasil|trans_title=Under-17s: Protagonist substitute, Nathan was decisive to Copa Brasil's title|publisher=Atlético Paranaense's official website|language=pt|date=22 July 2012|accessdate=15 April 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090358/http://www.atleticoparanaense.com/site/noticias/detalhe/27524/Sub-17-Reserva-protagonista-Nathan-foi-decisivo-para-o-ttulo-da-Copa-Brasil|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2014年他獲提升至一隊，最初代表U23球隊出戰[[巴拉納錦標賽|巴拉納錦標賽]]。

尼敦在2014年5月22日首次亮相[[巴甲|巴甲]]，在以1:1賽和[[哥連泰斯|哥連泰斯]]的聯賽中在下半場後備入替-{zh-cn:普利尼奥·迪亚斯; zh-tw:普利諾·迪亞斯; zh-hk:保連奴·戴亞斯}-（Paulinho Dias）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://globoesporte.globo.com/jogo/brasileirao2014/21-05-2014/corinthians-atletico-pr.html|title=Atlético-PR arranca empate com o Timão e frustra a Fiel mais uma vez|trans_title=Atlético-PR gets a draw against ''Timão'' and frustrates ''Fiel'' once more|publisher=Globo Esporte|language=pt|date=22 May 2014|accessdate=15 April 2015|archive-date=2014-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525025518/http://globoesporte.globo.com/jogo/brasileirao2014/21-05-2014/corinthians-atletico-pr.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在10月，他拒絕和球隊續約<ref>{{cite web|url=http://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/atletico-pr/noticia/2014/10/atletico-pr-tenta-renovar-contrato-de-nathan-mas-jogador-rejeita-proposta.html|title=Atlético-PR tenta renovar contrato de Nathan, mas jogador rejeita proposta|trans_title=Atlético-PR tries to renew Nathan's contract, but player rejects bid|publisher=Globo Esporte|language=pt|date=6 October 2014|accessdate=15 April 2015|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710014359/http://globoesporte.globo.com/pr/futebol/times/atletico-pr/noticia/2014/10/atletico-pr-tenta-renovar-contrato-de-nathan-mas-jogador-rejeita-proposta.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，結果他和球會對簿公堂，並將他降格回U23代表隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/atletico-pr/noticia/2014/12/jovem-do-atletico-pr-sofre-com-extra-campo-mas-garante-sei-o-que-quero.html#atleta-nathan|title=Jovem do Atlético-PR sofre com extra-campo, mas garante: "Sei o que quero"|trans_title=Atlético-PR's youngster suffers with outside, but assures: "I know what I want"|publisher=Globo Esporte|language=pt|date=10 December 2014|accessdate=15 April 2015|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710014358/http://globoesporte.globo.com/pr/futebol/times/atletico-pr/noticia/2014/12/jovem-do-atletico-pr-sofre-com-extra-campo-mas-garante-sei-o-que-quero.html#atleta-nathan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雖然從未為帕拉尼恩斯踢足全場90分鐘賽事<ref name=bleacher>{{cite web|url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2432541-chelsea-transfer-news-nathan-deal-doubted-latest-oscar-and-danny-rose-rumours|title=Chelsea Transfer News: Nathan Deal Doubted, Latest Oscar and Danny Rose Rumours|publisher=Bleacher Report|date=16 April 2015|accessdate=16 April 2015|first=Nick|last=Akerman|archive-date=2015-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150419025002/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2432541-chelsea-transfer-news-nathan-deal-doubted-latest-oscar-and-danny-rose-rumours|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但尼敦的表現成功吸引著名球會[[車路士|車路士]]和[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]的注視<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/570606/Brazil-Chelsea-wonderkid-4-5m-medical|title=Brazil wonderkid set to COMPLETE £4.5m Chelsea move TODAY|date=15 April 2015|accessdate=16 April 2015|archive-date=2015-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418000407/http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/570606/Brazil-Chelsea-wonderkid-4-5m-medical|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月10日，球會和車路士達成協議<ref>{{cite web|url=http://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/atletico-pr/noticia/2015/04/atletico-pr-e-nathan-fazem-acordo-e-meia-deve-defender-o-chelsea.html|title=Atlético-PR e Nathan fazem acordo e meia deve defender o Chelsea|trans_title=Atlético-PR and Nathan reach agreement and midfielder may play for Chelsea|publisher=Globo Esporte|language=pt|date=10 April 2015|accessdate=15 April 2015|archive-date=2015-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414024420/http://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/atletico-pr/noticia/2015/04/atletico-pr-e-nathan-fazem-acordo-e-meia-deve-defender-o-chelsea.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有傳這支倫敦球會付上450萬鎊收購他<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.com/story/2400108/chelsea-to-sign-brazil-and-atletico-paranaense-teenager-nathan-sources|title=Chelsea to sign Brazil and Atletico Paranaense teenager Nathan - sources|publisher=[[ESPN_FC|ESPN FC]]|date=15 April 2015|accessdate=15 April 2015|archive-date=2015-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418115223/http://www.espnfc.com/story/2400108/chelsea-to-sign-brazil-and-atletico-paranaense-teenager-nathan-sources|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月15日，尼敦在[[史丹福橋球場|史丹福橋球場]]進行了體測<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11668/9806928/sky-sources-brazilian-nathan-undergoing-chelsea-medical|title=Nathan to join Chelsea|publisher=Sky Sports|date=16 April 2015|accessdate=16 April 2015|archive-date=2015-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415224927/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11668/9806928/sky-sources-brazilian-nathan-undergoing-chelsea-medical|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===車路士===
2015年5月11日，尼敦在其[[Instagram|Instagram]]帳號表示他已跟2014/15球季英超聯的冠軍車路士簽約<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2892/transfer-zone/2015/05/11/11643022/brazilian-starlet-nathan-confirms-chelsea-move?CMPID=TWUK_150511_nathanchelsea/|last=|first=|title=Brazilian starlet Nathan confirms Chelsea move|date=11 May 2015|publisher=Goal|accessdate=11 May 2015|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130145302/https://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2892/transfer-zone/2015/05/11/11643022/brazilian-starlet-nathan-confirms-chelsea-move?CMPID=TWUK_150511_nathanchelsea%2F|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/576577/Chelsea-Nathan-Brazil?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter/|last=Chapman|first=Anthony|title=Chelsea sign Brazilian playmaker Nathan|date=11 May 2015|publisher=Express|accessdate=11 May 2015|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129071232/https://www.express.co.uk/sport/football/576577/Chelsea-Nathan-Brazil?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter%2F|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3077469/Nathan-signs-Chelsea-Brazilian-wonderkid-takes-Instagram-confirm-4-5million-deal-Jose-Mourinho-s-side.html?ITO=1490&ns_mchannel=rss&ns_campaign=1490&utm_medium=twitter&utm_source=twitterfeed|last=Ashton|first=Neil|title=Chelsea target Nathan confirms Blues signing with Instagram post and will join in £4.5million deal from Atletico Paranaense|publisher=Daily Mail|accessdate=11 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518103153/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3077469/Nathan-signs-Chelsea-Brazilian-wonderkid-takes-Instagram-confirm-4-5million-deal-Jose-Mourinho-s-side.html?ITO=1490&ns_mchannel=rss&ns_campaign=1490&utm_medium=twitter&utm_source=twitterfeed|dead-url=no}}</ref>。三日後，車路士亦官方宣布尼敦將會在7月1日正式加盟，轉會費未有公布，聲明亦指他已經通過體測及達成個人協議<ref>{{cite news|title=Nathan: Chelsea sign Brazilian midfielder for undisclosed fee|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32744221|accessdate=14 May 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=14 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150516101517/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32744221|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

尼敦在2015/16球季以及2016/17球季外借荷蘭的[[維迪斯職業足球基金會|维特斯]]，2017年夏天外借法國的[[艾米恩斯體育會|艾米恩斯]]。由於在[[艾米恩斯體育會|艾米恩斯]]上場機會不多，尼敦在2018年1月提早回到車路士，隨即外借到葡萄牙的[[貝倫人足球俱樂部|貝倫人]]到賽季結束。

==國際賽生涯==
尼敦同時是[[巴西17岁以下国家足球队|巴西U17国家隊]]和巴西U20代表隊成員。他在[[2013年U17世界盃足球賽|2013年U17世界盃足球賽]]首次代表U17球隊上陣，並在賽事中攻入五球，包括6:1大勝斯洛伐克包辦四球及擊敗主辦國阿聯酋的賽事中取得入球。尼敦入選為賽事最佳十一人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/tournaments/archive/u17worldcup/uae2013/index.html|title=2013 FIFA U17 World Cup - FIFA|publisher=FIFA|accessdate=2014-05-31|archive-date=2014-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011183838/http://www.fifa.com/tournaments/archive/u17worldcup/uae2013/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但球隊卻在半準決賽中被墨西哥淘汰出局。

他亦入選了在烏拉圭舉行的2015年南美洲青年錦標賽的大軍名單之中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://esporteinterativo.com.br/futebol-brasileiro/tecnico-alexandre-gallo-convoca-selecao-brasileira-que-disputara-o-sul-americano-sub-20/|title=Gallo convoca seleção brasileira que disputará o Sul-Americano sub-20|trans_title=Gallo calls up Brazil national team which will play in South American under-20|publisher=[[Esporte_Interativo|Esporte Interativo]]|language=pt|date=27 November 2014|accessdate=24 January 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128114022/http://esporteinterativo.com.br/futebol-brasileiro/tecnico-alexandre-gallo-convoca-selecao-brasileira-que-disputara-o-sul-americano-sub-20/|archivedate=2015年1月28日}}</ref>。尼敦在賽事中所有比賽均悉數上陣，並在2月4日大勝秘魯5:0的賽事中首次取得入球。

==比賽風格==
南美洲足球記者-{zh-cn:蒂姆·维克雷; zh-tw:蒂姆·維克利; zh-hk:添·域基利}-稱尼敦為可交出獨到傳球的[[組織核心|組織核心]]。他指尼敦雖然在U17代表隊表現出色，但在U20的表現卻低於平均水平，並難以理解尼敦如何憑去季的表現吸引車路士垂青。<ref name=bleacher/>

